10. KEY DECISIONS

10.1 Technology Choices

```
1. Build vs Buy:
   - 3D Engine: Build custom (control) vs Unity/Unreal (speed)
   - Decision: Start with Unity, migrate to custom

2. Open vs Closed:
   - Platform: Open API vs closed ecosystem
   - Decision: Open API with certification

3. Centralized vs Decentralized:
   - Storage: Centralized (performance) vs IPFS (resilience)
   - Decision: Hybrid approach
```

10.2 Business Model Choices

```
1. Pricing:
   - Options: Subscription vs transaction fee
   - Decision: Freemium + 15% transaction fee

2. Manufacturer Relations:
   - Options: Exclusive vs non-exclusive
   - Decision: Non-exclusive with quality tiers

3. IP Management:
   - Options: Platform ownership vs creator ownership
   - Decision: Creator ownership with platform license
```

